    <item>
      <title>比尔·阿克曼加大对《商业内幕》的攻势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/bill-ackman-urges-business-insider-to-correct-story-or-face-suit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁投资者比尔·阿克曼 (Bill Ackman) 就《商业内幕》指控其妻子抄袭的报道升级了对《商业内幕》的攻击，并部署了一家律师事务所向新闻媒体施加更大压力，要求其更正或撤回这些报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/bill-ackman-urges-business-insider-to-correct-story-or-face-suit</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 14:15:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
